OL,3,CSpecialist doctors vote to strike
OL,4,Clater in June
OL,6,FSpecialist doctors in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fhave voted to strike later in June
OL,8,Ffollowing a ballot for industrial
OL,9,Faction over pay.
OL,11,FThere were 90% of specialist,
OL,12,Fassociate specialist and specialty
OL,13,Fgrade (SAS) doctors which voted in
OL,14,Ffavour of strike action.
OL,16,FThey join consultant and resident
OL,17,Fdoctors who also voted to strike
OL,18,Fearlier this week.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
