FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1781387267
OL,3,CSpecialist doctors vote to strike
OL,4,Clater in June
OL,6,FIt means all doctors working in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's hospitals will be
OL,8,Fstaging walk-outs on June 25 and 29.
OL,10,FUTV understands that Stormont's Health
OL,11,FMinister Mike Nesbitt had a meeting
OL,12,Fwith British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,13,Fdoctors over a pay resolution on
OL,14,FThursday.
OL,16,FThe Department of Health described the
OL,17,Fengagement as useful and is keen to
OL,18,Fkeep the dialogue around pay open.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
