OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1781387267
OL,3,CSpecialist doctors vote to strike
OL,4,Clater in June
OL,6,FUTV understands no pay offer was made
OL,7,Ffor doctors to allow them to not
OL,8,Fstrike.
OL,10,FDr Leanne Davison, chair of BMA's
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland SAS committee
OL,12,F(NISASC), said: "SAS doctors do not
OL,13,Ftake the decision to strike lightly,
OL,14,Fand this result reflects the strength
OL,15,Fof feeling across our workforce about
OL,16,Fpay erosion.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
