PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1781387267
OL,3,CSpecialist doctors vote to strike
OL,4,Clater in June
OL,6,F"We are an essential part of the HSC
OL,7,Fworkforce, with experience comparable
OL,8,Fto our consultant and more senior
OL,9,Fresident doctor colleagues. Yet, like
OL,10,Fthem, we have seen our pay steadily
OL,11,Feroded since 2008.
OL,13,F"The persistent lack of recognition
OL,14,Fand limited opportunities for career
OL,15,Fprogression within the health service
OL,16,Fhave only compounded the sense that
OL,17,FSAS doctors are undervalued.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1781387267
OL,3,CSpecialist doctors vote to strike
OL,4,Clater in June
OL,6,F"This clear 'yes' vote shows that we
OL,7,Fhave reached a tipping point. SAS
OL,8,Fdoctors are prepared to stand up for
OL,9,Fthe future of the medical workforce
OL,10,Fand the care we provide to patients.
OL,12,F"Strike action is still avoidable. It
OL,13,Fis now up to the government to come
OL,14,Fforward with a meaningful and credible
OL,15,Foffer that makes real progress towards
OL,16,Fpay restoration."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
