OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1781387267
OL,3,CSpecialist doctors vote to strike
OL,4,Clater in June
OL,6,FMinister Nesbitt previously said he
OL,7,Fwas committed to implementing this
OL,8,Fyear's pay award, but is "currently
OL,9,Funable to do so in the absence of an
OL,10,FExecutive agreed budget".
OL,12,FHe also warned about financial
OL,13,Fpressures on the health budget and
OL,14,Fsaid it must be recognised that
OL,15,Ffinancial constraints mean there is no
OL,16,Froom for movement beyond the
OL,17,Frecommended 3.5% pay offer.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
